Package: herbCur
Title: An R package for curating plant biodiversity collections
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Domingos", "Cardoso", , "cardosobot@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7072-2656"))
Description: This package helps to automate the cleaning of herbarium records from public databases (e.g. GBIF, SEINet, and speciesLink) and generate herbarium labels from field books.
